Glosa Inter-Reti Diktionaria GID
– Centra, Deutsch –

Glosa is an international auxiliary language. For information, see www.glosa.org.

The list below shows

  • the most important Glosa words (the so called “Centra”-words, marked with “++”) of the Glosa Internet-Dictionary GID,
  • the English meanings of these Glosa words (like in the GID) and
  • a list of German translations to each English word.

The German translations have been made by means of the Linux program “steak”, version 1.7.3, by Razi Lotfi-Tabrizi.

Original URL of this file was: www.glosa.org/gid/gid_de.htm. Date: see end of this file.

Marcel Springer
